instruction: Design a house floor plan with three bedrooms and two bathrooms.
output: This floor plan has three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The main bedroom is located in the front left corner of the house, with a shared bathroom off to the side. The second bedroom is located in the back left corner, with another shared bathroom in the hallway. The third bedroom is located in the back right corner for the maximum privacy. The kitchen and the living area are in the center of the house for the easy access.
